    <briefdescription>
<para>Opt-in bare LOG_* aliases for the ICEBERG_LOG_* macros. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Separate opt-in header (not pulled in by <ref refid="logger_8h" kindref="compound">logger.h</ref> or <ref refid="log__macros_8h" kindref="compound">log_macros.h</ref>) so the short, unprefixed names never leak into consumers by default <ndash/> they would collide with glog/abseil/windows.h. Include this header explicitly to use them. No bare LOG(level) is provided. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
